WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.460
Why does the world's largest infrastructure provider actively invest in

00:00:04.460 --> 00:00:08.921
accelerating the sales of an independent software vendor? Mutual infrastructure

00:00:08.921 --> 00:00:13.381
growth drives the strategic alliance: as AppsFlyer scales, underlying cloud

00:00:13.381 --> 00:00:17.841
utilization increases, directly expanding AWS annual recurring revenue. Understanding this

00:00:17.841 --> 00:00:22.301
governing mechanism is your path to professional mastery in enterprise

00:00:22.301 --> 00:00:26.762
sales. The cloud computing ecosystem has transcended its origins as

00:00:26.762 --> 00:00:31.222
a mere technological sector to become the undisputed, foundational infrastructure

00:00:31.222 --> 00:00:35.682
of the modern global economy. Currently generating revenues well over

00:00:35.682 --> 00:00:40.143
one trillion dollars, this monumental industry is expanding at a

00:00:40.143 --> 00:00:44.603
relentless and compounding rate of twenty percent year over year.

00:00:44.603 --> 00:00:49.063
Financial institutions confidently project that this trajectory will only accelerate,

00:00:49.063 --> 00:00:53.523
driven heavily by the massive, resource-intensive rollout of artificial intelligence

00:00:53.523 --> 00:00:57.984
across all enterprise sectors, securely poising cloud revenues to exceed

00:00:57.984 --> 00:01:02.444
two trillion dollars by the year twenty-thirty.
